systems.name: Attila
systems.infos: Attila is a Feudal World of the Imperium of Man that maintains a late Iron Age civilisation and almost no advanced Imperial technology. This barbaric world is also the homeworld of the famed Rough Riders of Attila Mounted Regiments of the Imperial Guard.
